
Overview of adv once

The adv once has 3 senses (first 3 from tagged texts)
                                            
1. (98) once, one time, in one case -- (on one occasion; "once I ran into her")
2. (28) once -- (as soon as; "once we are home, we can rest")
3. (21) once, formerly, at one time, erstwhile, erst -- (at a previous time; "at one time he loved her"; "her erstwhile writing"; "she was a dancer once";)
